{"tid":1328033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醒下啦﹗你提修正案，即係助攻逃犯條件再上立法會呀﹗","createTime":"2019-07-17T19:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T20:39:24.000Z","uid":196430,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b016ca3986a651da110aac4f16f4f4b43cc47298","tid":1328033,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:52:07.000Z","msg":"根本唔係咩一次性嘅問題，而係你係對逃犯條件提出修正案，<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>政府就大條道理將議案再拎上立法會﹗</strong></span></span>我地係要<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撤回</strong></span></span>，而家竟然幫佢助攻？？？<br />\n<br />\n而且你覺得張超雄個所謂「一次性」方案會過到咩？我同你講，<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢幾年嚟泛民提嘅所有修正案，係無一條過到﹗係一條都無﹗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我就算當你過到，你真係覺得保皇狗唔會同政府夾計，<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再提多幾十項修訂改撚到你面目全非？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦﹗而家係對事不對人﹗而唔係分化﹗<br />\n<br />\n我理撚得張超雄係on9定係鬼，呢件事實在太嚴重﹗<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一定要佢收返個修正案先﹗</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d9bec654965d91c9c57469ea925a30c84c934614","tid":1328033,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:58:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c1938db65baabad327570589d00c9663bb5b7d5","tid":1328033,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T20:01:54.000Z","msg":"呢個係危 亦都係機<br />\n既然政府打算冷處理<br />\n我地咁樣撥返行個火唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢今日話唔傾 我地就係要逼佢傾"},{"pid":"73ad13221dcb07b838d37d54848285cb9392c938","tid":1328033,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1938db65baabad327570589d00c9663bb5b7d5","tid":1328033,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T20:01:54.000Z","msg":"呢個係危 亦都係機<br />\n既然政府打算冷處理<br />\n我地咁樣撥返行個火唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm